text: Chijioke is a given name. Notable people with the given name include: *Chijioke Amu-Nnadi (born 1962), Nigerian poet and author *Chijioke Ejiogu (born 1984), Nigerian soccer player *Chijioke Nwakodo, Nigerian politician and businessman *Chijioke Stephen Obioha (died 2016), Nigerian drug trafficker *Chijioke Onyenegecha (born 1983), Canadian football player
